56, "filesize_approx": 14118493, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/93.0.4577.82 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 1923.435, "format": "dash-763279630156668v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by erinmerylstudy", "description": "and the best part is you can try it right now! \n\nDon’t let anyone tell you that doodling is bad; it is actually one of the best tools you can use to help you get ‘in the zone’ when you’re focused and able to remember more 🧠 \n\nYou want to keep your doodling in the happy equilibrium between not too distracting but not under-stimulating ✏️ \n\n#doodle #studygram #doodling #studywithme #learning", "duration": 58.722, "timestamp": 1768911972, "uploader_id": "67658277539", "uploader": "erin meryl mcgurk", "channel": "erinmerylstudy", "like_count": 17529, "comment_count": 128, "comments": [{"author": "danielkarmy", "author_id": "242894815", "id": "18192802150360665", "text": "Im trying this to help with some diagnosed adhd feels 🙌 \n\nSimilarly, I have always noticed that writing on a physical calendar helps me remember better than tapping an event in to my phone diary.", "timestamp": 1774789891}, {"author": "aeldin26", "author_id": "1121729297", "id": "18084487463016562", "text": "This makes sense", "timestamp": 1774331465}, {"author": "_theblackssun", "author_id": "3062333280", "id": "18140938570498432", "text": "", "timestamp": 1774294439}, {"author": "kamallyall", "author_id": "864242395", "id": "17974702037868305", "text": "Im gonna try this", "timestamp": 1774259090}, {"author": "ashkr._.7", "author_id": "55990478388", "id": "17895419394280946", "text": "Thanks", "timestamp": 1774180066}, {"author": "prdp_j", "author_id": "823324968", "id": "18198197281341502", "text": "That's why you are worth following. Amazing share... ❤️", "timestamp": 1773642915}, {"author": "j4wad._.l", "author_id": "12810502836", "id": "17953580991094113", "text": "I had a habbit of walking around while carrying a book and studying . I think this is the same principle", "timestamp": 1773459865}, {"author": "jaykumarmandwale", "author_id": "66318109628", "id": "17903685339387434", "text": "Thanks👏", "timestamp": 1773405853}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/619132815_17918376210253540_6942010738629781381_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p640x640_sh0.08_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4zMjE2eDU3MTIuc2RyLmY4Mjc4Ny5kZWZhdWx0X2NvdmVyX2ZyYW1lLmMyIn0&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=104&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFY8ZS5fKqW9M2B_G8o1FSr4TGD_Zgkmju1PpdIQ_EX9_I7A_y5ATKrRzt0x9w4QDY&_nc_ohc=T5LxaiBtAbYQ7kNvwGHyY4b&_nc_gid=eyi7lz6yH0lp2PIT38anxQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af1FmBlFnkORNiPMwy2-LmZ26Y8AFAkGnQ90k3yJOkc4Hg&oe=69D7AED7&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/619132815_17918376210253540_6942010738629781381_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p750x750_sh0.08_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4zMjE2eDU3MTIuc2RyLmY4Mjc4Ny5kZWZhdWx0X2NvdmVyX2ZyYW1lLmMyIn0&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=104&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFY8ZS5fKqW9M2B_G8o1FSr4TGD_Zgkmju1PpdIQ_EX9_I7A_y5ATKrRzt0x9w4QDY&_nc_ohc=T5LxaiBtAbYQ7kNvwGHyY4b&_nc_gid=eyi7lz6yH0lp2PIT38anxQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af035pGAvlm7qm9WGa_oZzQCElkdSyu5sV4164Z9BJK8zg&oe=69D7AED7&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1332, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1332"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/619132815_17918376210253540_6942010738629781381_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh0.08_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4zMjE2eDU3MTIuc2RyLmY4Mjc4Ny5kZWZhdWx0X2NvdmV